@node Release @value{PACKAGE}-0.9.2.1
@unnumberedsubsec Major changes for release @value{PACKAGE}-0.9.2.1
@cindex release @value{PACKAGE}-0.9.2.1

This is the first release from @cite{The OpenSS7 Project} of the
@cite{@value{PACKAGE_TITLE}} package.  This package provides @file{dlgn},
@file{mercd} and @file{pmacd} device drivers, as well as a @file{dvbm} and
@file{sctmr} module.  Additional drivers are the @file{gncfd} and @file{gpio}
modules.  The package contains all the necessary manual pages and other
documentation for components in an autoconf tarball.

This release is the initial public release.

@itemize -
@item
In this initial release, the package already supports a wide range of production
distributions as it uses the same build environment as other OpenSS7 Project
packages.

@item
Added versions to all exported symbols.  Made LFS unique functions GPL export.

@item
Improvements to the common build environment with better support for standalone
package builds on 2.4 kernels.

@item
Support for most recent 2.6.18 kernels (including Fedora Core 5 with inode diet
patchset).

@end itemize

